title: Frog on Acorn
description: A vibrant green frog perched on a yellow acorn, surrounded by green leaves. The frog's bright color contrasts with the yellow and brown hues of the acorn, creating a striking image of nature.

title: Lone Tree in a Pastoral Landscape
description: A large, leafy tree stands prominently in a green pasture, surrounded by a stone wall. The sky is bright with a few clouds, and there are other smaller trees in the background, creating a serene rural scene.

title: Magnifying Glass
description: An illustration of a magnifying glass with a silver circular lens and a black handle.

title: Acorns and Leaves
description: A branch featuring two acorns and two green leaves. The acorns are brown with a light-colored cap, and the leaves are vibrant green with hints of yellow.

title: Magnifying Glass with Stand
description: A black magnifying glass with a stand, designed for hands-free use. The lens is circular and mounted on a rectangular base, which has a grid pattern for measuring or aligning objects.
